snippet.title: Dominating the skies Trailer
snippet.description:
Game is available now for FREE on mobile phones

iPhone:
https://apps.apple.com/sa/app/dominating-the-skies/id6444789260

Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.swipe_claw_games.dts_free

Or Buy the game on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1561670/Dominating_the_skies/?beta=0


Join our social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dominating.the.skies
discord: https://discord.gg/TThK8jQMjt


Description:​
Pilot a jet plane, helicopter and a spaceship.
Perform different missions, fight clever enemies, upgrade your aircraft, and much more.

Highlight:
- Physically accurate Flight Model.
- 55 levels.
- 4 different modes.
- 25 Amazing music tracks.

Supported inputs:
- Touchscreen
- Xbox controller
- Playstation controller
- Nintendo Switch controller
